Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type 'task mark-done 1'
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type 'task mark-in-progress 2'
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type 'task update 2 "Confirm release v1.0"'
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

